AFFIDAVIT OF NON-RECEIPT OF MAINTENANCE ASSESSMENTS
OF THE AMBER CREEK ASSOCIATION, INC.
STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF BEXAR
"Notice is hereby given that there exists a lien for unpaid maintenance assessments assessed by AMBER CREEK
ASSOCIATION, INC ., for non-payment by the owner of the subject property and such maintenance assessments being in
accordance with the Declaration of Covenants, Conditions, and Restrictions for Amber Creek Unit 1, as recorded in Volume
13240, Page 432 et seq. in the Official Public Records of Bexar County, Texas; First Amendment to the Declaration of
Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions for Amber Creek Unit 1, as recorded in Volume 15021, Page 60 et seq. in the Official
Public Records of Bexar County, Texas; and Third Supplement to the Declaration of Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions for
Amber Creek , Annexation of Unit 3, as recorded in Volume 16248, Page 873 et seq. in the Official Public Records of Bexar
County, Texas. The property subject to this Affidavit is as follows, to-wit:
SUBJECT PROPERTY:
Address:
Legal Description:
Last Known Owners:
Last Known Address:
Amount of Delinquent:
Assessments and Fees:
4326 Buckhorn Bayou, San Antonio, Texas 78245
Lot 62, Block 8, Amber Creek Unit 3 BSL, Bexar County, Texas, according to the
map or plat thereof recorded in Volume 9631, Page(s) 89 and replatted in Volume
9635, Page 173 Deed and Plat Records of Bexar County, Texas.
Benito Chavez and Leah M. Chavez
4326 Buckhorn Bayou, San Antonio, Texas 78245
$2,142.93
Amounts are subject to continued accrual of late fees, interest and collection costs
which shall be automatically added to the lien amount.
Executed this S day of January
_ 2022.
AMBER CREEK ASSOCIATION, INC.
By:
SPECTRUM ASSOCIATION MANAGEMENT, L.P.
By

San Antonio, Texas 78232

_2022, by JUAN M.
GARCIA, Legal Support Services of SPECTRUM ASSOCIATION MANAGEMENT, L.P ., on behalf of AMBER CREEK
ASSOCIATION, INC.
-

AFTER RECORDING, RETURN TO:
MICHAEL B. THURMAN
THURMAN & PHILLIPS, P.C.
4093 De Zavala Road
Shavano Park, Texas 78249
